{"id":748,"date":"2024-05-10T06:16:17","date_gmt":"2024-05-10T06:16:17","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/?p=748"},"modified":"2024-05-10T06:16:17","modified_gmt":"2024-05-10T06:16:17","slug":"commenting-sites-2024","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/commenting-sites-2024\/","title":{"rendered":"100+ Blog Commenting Sites 2024"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-rank-math-toc-block\" id=\"rank-math-toc\" id=\"rank-math-toc\"><p>Table of Contents<\/p><nav><ul><li ><a href=\"#top-blog-commenting-sites\">Top Blog Commenting Sites<\/a><\/li><li ><a href=\"#criteria-for-blog-commenting\">Criteria for Blog Commenting <\/a><\/li><li ><a href=\"#writing-blog-comment\">Writing Blog Comment <\/a><\/li><li ><a href=\"#finding-high-quality-blog-commenting-sites\">Finding  High-quality Blog Commenting Sites<\/a><\/li><li ><a href=\"#blog-commenting-sites-list-2024\">Blog Commenting Sites List 2024<\/a><ul><li ><a href=\"#blogging-seo-digital-marketing-blog\">Blogging, SEO, Digital Marketing Blog<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li ><a href=\"#education-blog-commenting-sites\">Education Blog Commenting Sites<\/a><\/li><li ><a href=\"#business-blog-commenting-sites\">Business Blog Commenting Sites<\/a><\/li><li ><a href=\"#other-blog-commenting-sites\">Other Blog Commenting Sites<\/a><\/li><li ><a href=\"#faq-top-blog-commenting-sites\">FAQ- Top Blog Commenting Sites<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"top-blog-commenting-sites\">Top Blog Commenting Sites<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Welcome to the realm of Blog Commenting Sites \u2013 a dynamic space where ideas, opinions, and conversations flourish. In the ever-expanding digital landscape, blogs have become a pivotal platform for individuals, businesses, and enthusiasts to share their thoughts and expertise. However, a blog&#8217;s true potential is often unlocked when readers engage in meaningful discussions through comments. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This symbiotic relationship between bloggers and their readers forms the backbone of online communities, fostering a vibrant exchange of viewpoints. In this article, we&#8217;ll delve into the significance of blog commenting sites, explore the benefits they offer, and provide you with a curated list of platforms where these enriching conversations come to life. Join us on a journey where every keystroke has the power to ignite conversations, connect minds, and shape perspectives.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"criteria-for-blog-commenting\">Criteria for Blog Commenting <\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Boosting Web Traffic: Unleash the power of blog commenting on authoritative platforms within your niche to drive an influx of curious visitors back to your own website. As your insightful comments resonate with readers, they&#8217;re more likely to follow the trail you&#8217;ve paved to explore what your website has to offer.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Forging Valuable Connections: Venture into the realm of blog commenting to cultivate meaningful relationships with fellow bloggers and key influencers in your field. Your thoughtful contributions can catch the discerning eye of not only the host blogger but also potential collaborators, opening doors to exciting partnerships and even guest posting opportunities.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Positioning Yourself as a Pro: Through your thought-provoking commentary, position yourself as a trusted authority in your industry. Crafting comments that offer genuine value showcases your expertise, bolstering your reputation and fostering a sense of credibility and reliance among your audience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Elevating SEO Standing: Engaging with esteemed blogs in your domain can earn you precious backlinks, a currency that holds immense sway in the realm of SEO. These backlinks from high domain authority blogs vouch for your website&#8217;s authenticity and excellence, ultimately contributing to your website&#8217;s higher search engine rankings.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Amplifying Brand Presence: Craft insightful and pertinent comments to ensure your brand stands out in the digital crowd. As your remarks capture readers&#8217; attention, your brand gains visibility, and recognition, creating a lasting imprint in the minds of potential customers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Broadening Perspectives: Dive into blog discussions to immerse yourself in a rich tapestry of diverse viewpoints. By engaging with varied perspectives, you broaden your intellectual horizons, stimulating personal and professional growth.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cultivating Digital Community: Participate actively in blog conversations to become an integral part of a virtual community. Sharing thoughts, exchanging experiences, and learning from others within this dynamic network can foster a sense of belonging and shared purpose.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Staying Abreast of Trends: Embrace the habit of regular blog reading and commenting to stay well-informed about industry trends, evolving ideas, and dynamic debates. This knowledge, freshly harvested from the latest discussions, can prove invaluable for shaping your own strategies and decisions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"writing-blog-comment\">Writing Blog Comment <\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Crafting a blog comment that gets approved quickly requires a combination of thoughtful engagement and adherence to the blog&#8217;s guidelines. Here&#8217;s a step-by-step guide on how to write a blog comment that is more likely to get approved swiftly:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Read the Post Carefully:<\/strong> Before commenting, read the blog post thoroughly to understand its content and context. Your comment should reflect that you&#8217;ve engaged with the material and are adding value to the discussion.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Be Relevant:<\/strong> Your comment should relate directly to the topic of the blog post. Avoid going off-topic or introducing unrelated subjects.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Add Value:<\/strong> Provide insights, opinions, or additional information that enhances the conversation. A well-thought-out comment contributes something meaningful to the discussion.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Be Respectful and Constructive:<\/strong> Maintain a respectful tone in your comment, even if you disagree with the author or other commenters. Constructive criticism is more likely to be approved than negative or inflammatory remarks.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Keep It Concise:<\/strong> While adding value is important, avoid making your comment too lengthy. A concise and focused comment is more likely to be read and approved quickly.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Engage with Others:<\/strong> Respond to other commenters as well. Engaging in a respectful and relevant conversation with fellow readers can demonstrate your genuine interest in the topic.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Avoid Self-Promotion:<\/strong> Most blogs frown upon blatant self-promotion in the comments section. While you can mention your expertise or experiences, avoid excessive linking to your own content or products.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Follow Guidelines:<\/strong> Some blogs have specific commenting guidelines. Make sure to adhere to these guidelines, which may include formatting, word count, or other specific requirements.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Use Real Identity:<\/strong> Use your real name or a consistent online identity when commenting. Anonymous or suspicious-looking usernames might raise red flags and delay approval.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Proofread:<\/strong> Ensure your comment is well-written, free of grammatical errors, and easy to understand. A polished comment is more likely to make a positive impression.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Use a Gravatar:<\/strong> If the blog uses Gravatars (Globally Recognized Avatars), having a profile picture associated with your email can lend credibility to your comment.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Be Timely:<\/strong> Comment relatively soon after the post is published. Early comments often receive more attention from both the blogger and other readers.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Check Back:<\/strong> Once you&#8217;ve submitted your comment, periodically check back to see if it has been approved or requires any modifications.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Remember, the primary goal of your comment should be to contribute meaningfully to the conversation. Approvals might vary from blog to blog, but by following these steps, you increase your chances of having your comment recognized and approved promptly.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"finding-high-quality-blog-commenting-sites\">Finding  High-quality Blog Commenting Sites<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Discovering high-quality blog commenting sites involves a mix of research and evaluation. Here&#8217;s a strategy to help you find reputable platforms for engaging in meaningful discussions through comments:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Identify Your Niche:<\/strong> Determine your industry or area of interest. Focusing on blogs within your niche ensures that your comments are relevant and valuable to the readers and authors.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Search Engines:<\/strong> Use search engines like Google to look for influential blogs in your niche. Use keywords related to your industry followed by terms like &#8220;top blogs,&#8221; &#8220;best blogs,&#8221; or &#8220;popular blogs.&#8221;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Social Media:<\/strong> Platforms like Twitter, LinkedIn, and Facebook can be great sources for discovering blogs shared by experts and influencers in your field.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Blog Directories:<\/strong> Online blog directories categorize blogs by topic, making it easier to find niche-specific blogs. Examples include AllTop, BlogLovin, and Technorati.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Content Aggregators:<\/strong> Websites like Reddit, Quora, and GrowthHackers have sections where users share and discuss blog posts. These can lead you to valuable blogs and discussions.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Competitor Research:<\/strong> Identify blogs where your competitors or industry leaders frequently comment. This indicates that these blogs are worth engaging with.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Guest Posts:<\/strong> Blogs that accept guest posts often have active communities and could be good options for commenting. Look for a &#8220;Write for Us&#8221; or &#8220;Contribute&#8221; section on their websites.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Influencers&#8217; Blogs:<\/strong> Explore blogs of influencers in your niche. If they allow comments, engaging there can help you get noticed by a larger audience.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Check Comments on Blogs You Read:<\/strong> If you already read blogs in your niche, check out the comments section. You might find valuable blogs where insightful discussions take place.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Evaluate Engagement:<\/strong> Look for blogs with an active and engaged readership. The number of comments, replies, and interactions can indicate the level of community involvement.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Quality of Content:<\/strong> Prioritize blogs that consistently publish high-quality, well-researched, and informative content. Blogs that value quality often attract a thoughtful readership.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Domain Authority:<\/strong> Use tools like Moz&#8217;s Domain Authority or Ahrefs to gauge the authority of the blog. Blogs with higher domain authority tend to have a larger and more engaged audience.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Check Commenting Policies:<\/strong> Before investing time in commenting, review the blog&#8217;s commenting policies. Some blogs have strict guidelines or moderation processes.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Engagement Level:<\/strong> If bloggers and authors actively reply to comments, it&#8217;s a positive sign of a community that values interaction.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Personal Connections:<\/strong> Reach out to fellow professionals or friends in your industry and ask for recommendations on blogs they find valuable for engagement.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"blog-commenting-sites-list-2024\">Blog Commenting Sites List 2024<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The link to the  Blog commenting site is provided  below:<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>https:\/\/docs.google.com\/spreadsheets\/d\/1uWK5pZJSV-DqsSBTXxBzWXSXsdccqurAd0iru3cr5CU\/edit?usp=sharing<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"blogging-seo-digital-marketing-blog\"><strong>Blogging, SEO, Digital Marketing Blog<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>https:\/\/www.elegantthemes.com\/blog<\/td><td>90<\/td><td>94<\/td><td>3<\/td><td><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>2<\/td><td>https:\/\/neilpatel.com\/blog<\/td><td>90<\/td><td>91<\/td><td>1<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>3<\/td><td>https:\/\/yoast.com\/seo-blog<\/td><td>84<\/td><td>90<\/td><td>1<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>4<\/td><td>https:\/\/problogger.com\/blog<\/td><td>83<\/td><td>81<\/td><td>1<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>5<\/td><td>https:\/\/copyblogger.com\/blog<\/td><td>81<\/td><td>86<\/td><td>1<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>6<\/td><td>https:\/\/www.shoutmeloud.com\/blog<\/td><td>77<\/td><td>79<\/td><td>1<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>7<\/td><td>https:\/\/www.quicksprout.com<\/td><td>73<\/td><td>86<\/td><td>0<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>8<\/td><td>https:\/\/backlinko.com\/blog<\/td><td>71<\/td><td>90<\/td><td>4<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>9<\/td><td>https:\/\/wptavern.com<\/td><td>63<\/td><td>83<\/td><td>7<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>10<\/td><td>https:\/\/www.smartpassiveincome.com\/blog<\/td><td>62<\/td><td>80<\/td><td>1<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>11<\/td><td>https:\/\/smartblogger.com\/blog<\/td><td>61<\/td><td>79<\/td><td>1<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>12<\/td><td>https:\/\/johnchow.com\/blog<\/td><td>60<\/td><td>72<\/td><td>18<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>13<\/td><td>https:\/\/www.junglescout.com\/blog<\/td><td>59<\/td><td>78<\/td><td>2<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>14<\/td><td>https:\/\/www.advancedwebranking.com\/blog<\/